.TH "RTCTRANSPORTSTATS.SELECTEDCANDIDATEPAIRCHANGES" "3JS" "June 24, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
RTCTransportStats.selectedCandidatePairChanges \- RTCTransportStats:
selectedCandidatePairChanges property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]selectedCandidatePairChanges\f[B]\f[R] property of the
\f[CR]RTCTransportStats\f[R] dictionary indicates the total number of
times that the selected candidate pair of this transport has changed.
.SH VALUE
A positive integer that is initially zero and increases whenever a
candidate pair is selected or lost.
